<i>♪ ♪</i>

15:41.002 --> 15:44.303
<i>♪ I can't be ♪</i>

15:44.305 --> 15:48.507
<i>♪ Everything you
want me to be ♪</i>

15:48.509 --> 15:51.544
<i>♪ I can't be ♪</i>

15:51.546 --> 15:55.514
<i>♪ Everything you
want me to be ♪</i>

15:55.516 --> 15:58.851
<i>♪ Finally ♪</i>

15:58.853 --> 16:02.888
<i>♪ I can see the light
through the leaves ♪</i>

16:02.890 --> 16:06.025
<i>♪ But it's all gone ♪</i>

