<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:17.705 --> 16:20.840
<i>♪ But it's all gone ♪</i>

16:20.842 --> 16:25.077
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:25.079 --> 16:28.214
<i>♪ But it's all gone ♪</i>

16:28.239 --> 16:31.442
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:31.444 --> 16:34.812
[firecrackers popping and whistling]

16:36.190 --> 16:38.424
[laughs]

16:38.426 --> 16:44.930
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:44.932 --> 16:47.840
[gunshots]

16:48.914 --> 16:51.370
[car alarm blaring]

16:51.372 --> 16:58.244
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:58.686 --> 17:00.246
Well, there you go, Pop.

17:00.704 --> 17:02.755
We give you one Detroit sunrise.

17:03.131 --> 17:05.555
Yeah, it's one of my favorite places.

17:06.286 --> 17:07.653
I used to take you guys fishing here.

17:08.089 --> 17:09.888
Yeah, Mr. Cramblin. You sure did.

17:09.891 --> 17:12.090
I caught a carp the size of my head.

17:12.093 --> 17:13.792
[laughs]

17:14.115 --> 17:15.380
I remember that.

17:15.405 --> 17:17.672
Took turns reeling that sucker in.

17:20.364 --> 17:23.332
[howls]

17:33.095 --> 17:34.847
We for sure got to get back.

17:34.849 --> 17:36.182
Yeah.

17:41.030 --> 17:44.031
<i>♪ ♪</i>

17:44.032 --> 17:46.366
Boys, thanks for a great night.

17:46.368 --> 17:48.201
It's our pleasure, Mr. Cramblin.

17:48.203 --> 17:50.582
Sam, you can call me Hank.

17:51.172 --> 17:56.445
<i>♪ ♪</i>

17:58.146 --> 17:59.759
It was great to see you, Dad.

18:00.482 --> 18:02.098
I'll come visit this weekend.

18:02.350 --> 18:03.471
I'd like that.

18:03.852 --> 18:05.184
Yeah, we actually have to get

18:05.186 --> 18:06.786
to that Husky Boys shoot.

18:06.788 --> 18:08.688
I know it's just small potatoes, but...

18:08.690 --> 18:10.523
Ah, small potatoes, big potatoes.

18:10.525 --> 18:12.163
Hey, it's food on the table.

18:12.623 --> 18:13.651
Proud of you.

18:14.496 --> 18:15.828
Thanks, Dad.

18:15.830 --> 18:18.237
You know, there's something
I've been wanting to tell you.

18:18.262 --> 18:19.694
The meeting at Hudson's?

18:19.719 --> 18:21.775
- Yeah.
- The shit in the briefcase?

18:22.170 --> 18:23.192
Yeah.

18:24.172 --> 18:25.719
Wasn't my shit.

18:27.375 --> 18:29.309
I think that actually
makes it worse, Dad.

18:29.311 --> 18:30.843
- It does?
- Yeah.

18:30.845 --> 18:32.026
Hmm.

18:32.134 --> 18:34.291
Well, Sam.

18:35.151 --> 18:36.100
Hank.

18:37.152 --> 18:38.851
- Son.
- Dad.

18:38.853 --> 18:40.353
- Love you.
- Love you too.

18:49.766 --> 18:52.532
- Did he say it wasn't his shit?
- Yeah.

18:52.534 --> 18:54.100
I mean, that makes it worse, doesn't it?

18:54.102 --> 18:55.368
Yeah, no, that's what I told him.

18:55.370 --> 18:56.703
That's exactly what I told him.

18:56.705 --> 18:59.170
Husky Jeans, skinny prices.

18:59.171 --> 19:01.338
Yup, I mean, that's it.

19:01.340 --> 19:02.230
Thanks, Dad.

19:02.269 --> 19:03.473
I'll send you a bill.

19:03.475 --> 19:05.308
See you in the funny pages.

19:06.879 --> 19:08.124
You okay?

19:08.247 --> 19:09.289
Yeah.

19:09.414 --> 19:11.377
It was actually a great day.

19:12.551 --> 19:15.933
It's like we were spending time
with the best version of my dad.

19:16.789 --> 19:20.585
There was no anger,
fits of rage, paranoia.

19:20.893 --> 19:22.559
- Hey, hey, hey, hey!
- Fecal hoarding.

19:22.561 --> 19:24.427
Hank! Hey, Hank! Come on! Come on, Hank!

19:24.429 --> 19:26.924
Maybe he is actually getting better.

19:27.942 --> 19:29.332
I'm gonna talk to doctors this week,

19:29.334 --> 19:30.844
see if he can get out.

19:31.370 --> 19:32.936
He could maybe even come and help us out

19:32.938 --> 19:34.272
a few times a week in the office.

19:34.297 --> 19:35.939
- That'd be great.
- It'd be awesome.

19:35.941 --> 19:37.641
Hey, can I buy you breakfast?

19:37.643 --> 19:39.576
No, you can't, 'cause
I'm buying you breakfast.

19:39.578 --> 19:41.144
Don't do that, Tim.

19:41.146 --> 19:42.846
You know, when you don't
let me pay for stuff,

19:42.848 --> 19:44.714
it's like your way of controlling me.

19:44.716 --> 19:46.550
Controlling you? I'm being nice.

19:46.552 --> 19:48.385
- Yeah, right.
- [Hank laughing]

19:48.387 --> 19:50.554
How's buying you breakfast not nice?

19:50.556 --> 19:52.589
- Don't do this, man!
- Tim, it's systemic racism.

19:52.591 --> 19:54.858
We're fat, man! Come on, slow down.

